HEADWORD: Hydrobranchiata
<hw>Hy`dro*bran`chi*a"ta</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <grk>"y`dwr</grk> water + <?/ gills.]</ety>
